The Road to Guantanamo;;83;;86;;R;;In September 2001 several British Muslim friends go to Pakistan to attend a wedding. They decide to visit Afghanistan, but they find Kandahar under attack and flee to Kabul. From there the friends try to return to Pakistan but mistakenly end up in a Taliban stronghold. Following their capture, they are sent to a U.S. military base in Cuba, where they endure torture.;;War,Drama;;Michael Winterbottom,Mat Whitecross;;2006;;Riz Ahmed,Farhad Harun,Waqar Siddiqui,Afran Usman,Shahid Iqbal,Mark Holden,Duane Henry,Adam James;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/road_to_guantanamo